OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781330678
OL,3,CBritish artist David Hockney dies,
OL,4,Caged 88
OL,6,FCelebrated British painter David
OL,7,FHockney has died aged 88.
OL,9,FA statement by his publicist described
OL,10,Fhim as "one of the most important
OL,11,Ffigures in contemporary art in both
OL,12,Fthe 20th and 21st centuries".
OL,14,FIt added that he passed away
OL,15,F"peacefully at home on 11 June 2026,
OL,16,Fone month short of his 89th birthday".
OL,18,FTributes are being paid from the art
OL,19,Fworld, with Dame Tracey Emin saying
OL,20,Fshe feels "very privileged" to have
OL,21,Fknown Hockney.
OL,26,@rD@HOUtD@\O]wD@AOUxD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/22
