OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781330678
OL,3,CBritish artist David Hockney dies,
OL,4,Caged 88
OL,6,F"A great artist and a wonderful man,
OL,7,Fwho with the power of art changed the
OL,8,Fperception of Britishness. A proud
OL,9,Fchain-smoking homosexual, who flew the
OL,10,Fflag higher than any other British
OL,11,Fartist," she said.
OL,13,FOver the course of more than seven
OL,14,Fdecades, Hockney's joyful and
OL,15,Foptimistic vision made him one of the
OL,16,Fworld's most popular artists.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
