OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781330678
OL,3,CBritish artist David Hockney dies,
OL,4,Caged 88
OL,6,FFrom the azure blue swimming pools of
OL,7,FCalifornia to the lush green
OL,8,Flandscapes of his native Yorkshire,
OL,9,FHockney's paintings were filled with
OL,10,Fcolour and light.
OL,12,FWhile liberally drawing on the art of
OL,13,Fthe past ` from the Renaissance
OL,14,Fmasters to the abstract expressionism
OL,15,Fof Jackson Pollock ` he consistently
OL,16,Fpursued his own path, refusing to
OL,17,Fconform to the artistic fashions of
OL,18,Fthe day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
