PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781330678
OL,3,CBritish artist David Hockney dies,
OL,4,Caged 88
OL,6,FAs an art school rebel, he was
OL,7,Finitially denied a diploma, in part
OL,8,Fbecause he refused to complete an
OL,9,Fessay assignment, insisting he should
OL,10,Fbe judged on his artwork alone.
OL,12,FAt the start of his career, at a time
OL,13,Fwhen more abstract styles dominated,
OL,14,FHockney bucked the trend ` painting
OL,15,Ffiguratively, often in bright colours
OL,16,Fwith a primitivist style.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
