PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781330678
OL,3,CBritish artist David Hockney dies,
OL,4,Caged 88
OL,6,FYears later, when some critics decried
OL,7,Fhis embrace of landscape painting as a
OL,8,Fretrograde step, he made clear he
OL,9,F"didn't give a damn" about such
OL,10,Fcriticisms.
OL,12,FHis subjects extended well beyond
OL,13,Flandscapes ` painting countless still
OL,14,Flifes, and portraits of friends family
OL,15,Fand even his pet dachshunds ` as well
OL,16,Fas stage designs for theatre and opera.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
