PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781330678
OL,3,CBritish artist David Hockney dies,
OL,4,Caged 88
OL,6,FHe was also fascinated by the
OL,7,Fpotential for technology to produce
OL,8,Fart: Making large-scale photo collages
OL,9,Fusing Polaroid prints in the 1980s,
OL,10,Fand using the Brushes app to create
OL,11,Fhundreds of pictures on his iPad in
OL,12,Fthe 2000s.
OL,14,FHaving grown up under the northern
OL,15,Fskies of industrial Bradford, Hockney
OL,16,Fwas enthralled by the light and
OL,17,Ffreedoms of 1960s California, making
OL,18,Fthe state his main home for 40 years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
