OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781330678
OL,3,CBritish artist David Hockney dies,
OL,4,Caged 88
OL,6,FA lifelong smoker, rarely seen without
OL,7,Fa cigarette in hand, Hockney would
OL,8,Fregularly rail against those who
OL,9,Fsought to clampdown on the practice.
OL,11,FIn his 80s, he even had badges made
OL,12,Fwith the slogan "End bossiness soon" `
OL,13,Fhe quipped that a demand to "End
OL,14,Fbossiness now" would be just "too
OL,15,Fbossy".
OL,17,FBorn in Bradford on July 9, 1937,
OL,18,FHockney was the fourth of five
OL,19,Fchildren in a working class family.
OL,26,@tD@QOUtD@dO]uD@]OUvD@NO]vD@^OUwD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
