OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781330678
OL,3,CBritish artist David Hockney dies,
OL,4,Caged 88
OL,6,FHis father, Kenneth, was an
OL,7,Faccountant's clerk who painted "Ban
OL,8,Fthe Bomb" posters for local peace
OL,9,Fmarchers, while his mother Laura was a
OL,10,FMethodist and strict vegetarian.
OL,12,FAt the age of just 11 he decided he
OL,13,Fwanted to be an artist, an ambition
OL,14,Fwhich was not encouraged by his
OL,15,Fteachers at Bradford Grammar School,
OL,16,Fbut with the support of his parents,
OL,17,Fhe entered the local art college.
OL,26,@oD@`OUpD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
