OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781330678
OL,3,CBritish artist David Hockney dies,
OL,4,Caged 88
OL,6,FFrom there he went to the Royal
OL,7,FCollege of Art in London where he was
OL,8,Fmocked for his Yorkshire accent ` but
OL,9,Ffor his part, he was not impressed by
OL,10,Fthe artistic abilities of his
OL,11,Ftormentors.
OL,13,F"I'd look at their drawings and think
OL,14,Fif I drew like that I'd keep my mouth
OL,15,Fshut," he later recalled.
OL,17,FThere was a memorable run-in with the
OL,18,Fcollege authorities when he was warned
OL,19,Fthat he could not graduate ` in part
OL,20,Fbecause he had not done enough life
OL,21,Fdrawings.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/22
