OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781330678
OL,3,CBritish artist David Hockney dies,
OL,4,Caged 88
OL,6,FHe responded by producing Life
OL,7,FPainting for a Diploma, featuring a
OL,8,Fmale nude copied from an American body-
OL,9,Fbuilding magazine alongside an
OL,10,Fanatomical study of a human skeleton.
OL,12,FIn the face of such an overwhelming
OL,13,Ftalent the college backed down,
OL,14,Fawarding him the prestigious gold
OL,15,Fmedal for painting ` which he
OL,16,Fcollected in suitably flamboyant
OL,17,Ffashion dressed in a gold lame suit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
