OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781330678
OL,3,CBritish artist David Hockney dies,
OL,4,Caged 88
OL,6,FIn contrast to drab, buttoned-up post-
OL,7,Fwar Britain, he was from the start
OL,8,Fintoxicated by both the brilliant
OL,9,Fsunlight and hedonistic freedoms he
OL,10,Ffound in California after moving to
OL,11,FLos Angeles in 1964.
OL,13,F"The moment I got to America I thought
OL,14,F'This is the place'," he later
OL,15,Frecalled.
OL,17,F"I was drawn towards California, which
OL,18,FI didn't know... because I sensed the
OL,19,Fplace would excite me. No doubt it had
OL,20,Fa lot to do with sex."
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@UO]yD@AOU|D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
