PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781330678
OL,3,CBritish artist David Hockney dies,
OL,4,Caged 88
OL,6,FAfter taking a job teaching drawing at
OL,7,Fthe University of California at Santa
OL,8,FCruz, he began a relationship with a
OL,9,F17-year-old student, Peter
OL,10,FSchlesinger, who also became his muse.
OL,12,FIt was in this period ` influenced by
OL,13,Fthe hard clean lines and vivid colours
OL,14,Fof American pop artists like Roy
OL,15,FLichtenstein ` that he produced some
OL,16,Fof his most famous works.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
