OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781330678
OL,3,CBritish artist David Hockney dies,
OL,4,Caged 88
OL,6,FUsing the comparatively new acrylic
OL,7,Fmedium, with strong, vibrant colours,
OL,8,Fhe created a series of striking images
OL,9,Fof swimming pools ` most notably A
OL,10,FBigger Splash ` which seemed to
OL,11,Fencapsulate the allure of the state he
OL,12,Fcalled the "promised land".
OL,14,FHe also painted one of the best-known
OL,15,Fof his many portraits ` Mr and Mrs
OL,16,FClark and Percy ` depicting his
OL,17,Ffriends, the fashion designers Celia
OL,18,FBirtwell and Ossie Clark, with their
OL,19,Fpet cat.
OL,26,@tD@LOUtD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
