PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781330678
OL,3,CBritish artist David Hockney dies,
OL,4,Caged 88
OL,6,FDespite his years in the States, he
OL,7,Finsisted he had always felt "very
OL,8,FEnglish".
OL,10,FHe said: "I'm from the peasantry,
OL,11,Ffrankly. But it makes you connect with
OL,12,Fthe land and because I found this
OL,13,Fsubject, at my age it's terrific, you
OL,14,Fstick with it and get turned on."
OL,16,FHe eventually returned full-time,
OL,17,Fsetting up home in the seaside resort
OL,18,Fof Bridlington, while going out to
OL,19,Fpaint the surrounding countryside en
OL,20,Fplein air using both oils and
OL,21,Fwatercolours.
OL,26,@oD@]OUpD@HO]rD@JOUvD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
