OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781330678
OL,3,CBritish artist David Hockney dies,
OL,4,Caged 88
OL,6,FHis works from this time included the
OL,7,Fmassive Bigger Trees Near Warter, an
OL,8,Foil painting more than 12 metres wide,
OL,9,Fmade up of 50 panels, which he
OL,10,Fcompleted in 2007.
OL,12,FIn 2012, an exhibition at the Royal
OL,13,FAcademy focusing on his Yorkshire
OL,14,Flandscapes, entitled A Bigger Picture,
OL,15,Fwas a smash hit attracting 600,000
OL,16,Fvisitors, effectively confirming his
OL,17,Fstatus as the country's best-loved
OL,18,Fliving artist.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
