OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781330678
OL,3,CBritish artist David Hockney dies,
OL,4,Caged 88
OL,6,FIt also highlighted his growing use of
OL,7,Ftechnology, including iPad drawings
OL,8,Fand a series of films produced using
OL,9,F18 cameras which were displayed on
OL,10,Fmultiple screens.
OL,12,FTragedy struck the following year when
OL,13,Fhis 23-year-old assistant, Dominic
OL,14,FElliott, died after drinking a
OL,15,Fhousehold drain cleaner at the
OL,16,Fartist's home having first consumed a
OL,17,Fpowerful cocktail of drugs and alcohol.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
