OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781330678
OL,3,CBritish artist David Hockney dies,
OL,4,Caged 88
OL,6,FAn inquest heard Hockney, who had
OL,7,Fbecome increasingly deaf, had slept
OL,8,Fthrough it, unaware of what was
OL,9,Fhappening. In the aftermath he
OL,10,Freturned to California.
OL,12,FHaving once declined the opportunity
OL,13,Fto paint Queen Elizabeth II, he
OL,14,Fclaimed he was "too busy" painting
OL,15,FEngland ` "her country", he
OL,16,Fnevertheless found time to design a
OL,17,Fstained-glass window at Westminster
OL,18,FAbbey in tribute to her.
OL,26,@vD@POUvD@YO]wD@KOUwD@WO]
