OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781330678
OL,3,CBritish artist David Hockney dies,
OL,4,Caged 88
OL,6,FUnveiled in 2018, it marked her love
OL,7,Fof the countryside with a scene of
OL,8,FHawthorn blossom from his native
OL,9,FYorkshire. "I hope she'll like it," he
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FThat same year, Hockney's painting,
OL,13,FPortrait of an Artist (Pool with Two
OL,14,FFigures), was sold at auction in New
OL,15,FYork for $90 million dollars (#70
OL,16,Fmillion) ` smashing the then record
OL,17,Ffor a work by a living artist.
