OL,3,CBritish artist David Hockney dies,
OL,4,Caged 88
OL,6,FAt the age of 87, the Fondation Louis
OL,7,FVuitton in Paris staged the largest
OL,8,Fexhibition yet of his art, with more
OL,9,Fthan 450 works ` the majority from the
OL,10,Fpreceding 25 years ` filling the
OL,11,Fentire museum, much to his obvious
OL,12,Fpleasure.
OL,14,FHis health by this stage was in
OL,15,Fserious decline and he required round-
OL,16,Fthe-clock nursing care, but
OL,17,Fnevertheless, he remained resolutely
OL,18,Fupbeat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/22
