OL,3,CBritish artist David Hockney dies,
OL,4,Caged 88
OL,6,FClaiming his loss of hearing had
OL,7,Fsharpened his work, he said: "If you
OL,8,Flose one sense, you gain other senses,
OL,9,Fand I feel I could see space clearer."
OL,11,FHockney never lost his love of
OL,12,Fpainting, continuing to work for four
OL,13,Fto six hours a day.J"I'm happiest when
OL,14,FI'm painting," he said. "If I can
OL,15,Fpaint every day I don't care about
OL,16,Fanything else."
